iv class="line">15:04:00 SQL&gt; SELECT current_scn FROM v$database;</div><div class="line">SELECT current_scn FROM v$database      =&gt;错误原因：需要dba权限</div><div class="line">                        *</div><div class="line">第 1 行出现错误:</div><div class="line">ORA-00942: table or view does not exist</div><div class="line"></div><div class="line">15:05:02 SQL&gt; conn system/aaa;          =&gt;切换用户system查询</div><div class="line">已连接。</div><div class="line">15:08:21 SQL&gt; SELECT current_scn FROM v$database;</div><div class="line"></div><div class="line">CURRENT_SCN</div><div class="line">-----------</div><div class="line">     753183                         =&gt;最近commit的SCN</div><div class="line"></div><div class="line">15:08:31 SQL&gt; conn scott/oracle1994;</div><div class="line">已连接。</div><div class="line">15:09:10 SQL&gt; update test set name='LIU' where id=1;</div><div class="line"></div><div class="line">已更新 1 行。</div><div class="line"></div><div class="line">15:09:51 SQL&gt; commit;</div><div class="line"></div><div class="line">提交完成。</div><div class="line"></div><div class="line">15:10:01 SQL&gt; select * from test;</div><div class="line"></div><div class="line">        ID NAME</div><div class="line">---------- --------------------</div><div class="line">         1 LIU</div><div class="line">         2 ZHAO</div><div class="line">         3 WANG</div><div class="line"></div><div class="line">15:10:22 SQL&gt; delete from test where id=3;</div><div class="line"></div><div class="line">已删除 1 行。</div><div class="line"></div><div class="line">15:10:47 SQL&gt; commit;</div><div class="line"></div><div class="line">提交完成。</div><div class="line"></div><div class="line">15:10:56 SQL&gt; select * from test;</div><div class="line"></div><div class="line">        ID NAME</div><div class="line">---------- --------------------</div><div class="line">         1 LIU</div><div class="line">         2 ZHAO</div><div class="line"></div><div class="line"></div><div class="line"></div><div class="line">15:11:05 SQL&gt; alter table test ENABLE ROW MOVEMENT;      =&gt;启动test表的ROW MOVEMENT特性</div><div class="line">				</div><div class="line">表已更改。</div><div class="line"></div><div class="line">15:12:20 SQL&gt; FLASHBACK TABLE test TO TIMESTAMP        =&gt;将test表恢复到2017-5-23 </div><div class="line">15:13:00   2  TO_TIMESTAMP('2017-5-23 15:10:47',         15:10:47时刻的状态</div><div class="line">15:15:19   3  'YYYY-MM-DD HH24:MI:SS');</div><div class="line"></div><div class="line">闪回完成。</div><div class="line"></div><div class="line">15:16:00 SQL&gt; select * from test;</div><div class="line"></div><div class="line">        ID NAME</div><div class="line">---------- --------------------</div><div class="line">         1 LIU</div><div class="line">         2 ZHAO</div><div class="line">         3 WANG</div><div class="line"></div><div class="line">15:16:14 SQL&gt; FLASHBACK TABLE test TO SCN 753183;        =&gt;将test表恢复到SCN为753183的状态时刻</div><div class="line"></div><div class="line">闪回完成。</div><div class="line"></div><div class="line">15:17:40 SQL&gt; select * from test;</div><div class="line"></div><div class="line">        ID NAME</div><div class="line">---------- --------------------</div><div class="line">         1 ZHANG</div><div class="line">         2 ZHAO</div><div class="line">         3 WANG</div></pre></td></tr></table></figure>
<hr>
<ul>
<li><strong>闪回删除可恢复使用DROP TABLE语句删除的表，是一种对意外删除的表的恢复机制。</strong></li>
<li><strong>闪回删除功能的实现主要是通过Oracle 10g数据库中的“回收站”（Recycle Bin）技术实现的。</strong></li>
<li><strong>在Oracle 10g数据库中，当执行DROP TABLE操作时，并不立即回收表及其关联对象的空间，而是将它们重命名后放入一个称为“回收站”的逻辑容器中保存，直到用户决定永久删除它们或存储该表的表空间存储空间不足时，表才真正被删除。</strong></li>
<li><strong>为了使用闪回删除技术，必须开启数据库的“回收站”。</strong></li>
</ul>
