">15:21:41 SQL&gt; drop table test;</div><div class="line"></div><div class="line">表已删除。</div><div class="line">15:23:51 SQL&gt;  conn scott/oracle1994;</div><div class="line">已连接。</div><div class="line">15:24:33 SQL&gt; select OBJECT_NAME,ORIGINAL_NAME,TYPE      =&gt;通过USER_RECYCLEBIN</div><div class="line">15:25:12   2  FROM USER_RECYCLEBIN;                        查看回收站信息</div><div class="line"></div><div class="line">OBJECT_NAME                    ORIGINAL_NAME</div><div class="line">------------------------------ --------------------------------</div><div class="line">TYPE</div><div class="line">-------------------------</div><div class="line">BIN$U7+8NB2MT7evMqzuXc91UQ==$0 SYS_C006599</div><div class="line">INDEX</div><div class="line"></div><div class="line">BIN$+pzajLDST0qgKVLj7zzhhw==$0 TEST</div><div class="line">TABLE</div><div class="line"></div><div class="line">15:25:18 SQL&gt; conn system/aaa;</div><div class="line">已连接。</div><div class="line">15:28:13 SQL&gt; select OBJECT_NAME,ORIGINAL_NAME,TYPE       =&gt;通过DBA_RECYCLEBIN</div><div class="line">15:28:21   2  FROM DBA_RECYCLEBIN;                          查看回收站信息</div><div class="line"></div><div class="line">OBJECT_NAME                    ORIGINAL_NAME</div><div class="line">------------------------------ --------------------------------</div><div class="line">TYPE</div><div class="line">-------------------------</div><div class="line">BIN$U7+8NB2MT7evMqzuXc91UQ==$0 SYS_C006599</div><div class="line">INDEX</div><div class="line"></div><div class="line">BIN$+pzajLDST0qgKVLj7zzhhw==$0 TEST</div><div class="line">TABLE</div><div class="line"></div><div class="line"></div><div class="line">15:28:37 SQL&gt; conn scott/oracle1994;</div><div class="line">已连接。</div><div class="line">15:32:08 SQL&gt; select * from "BIN$+pzajLDST0qgKVLj7zzhhw==$0";  </div><div class="line">                                                         =&gt;通过表在回收站中的新名</div><div class="line">        ID NAME                                            字查询表中的数据</div><div class="line">---------- --------------------</div><div class="line">         1 ZHANG</div><div class="line">         2 ZHAO</div><div class="line">         3 WANG</div></pre></td></tr></table></figure>
